        "overview_item_data_type": "list",
        "overview_item_data_items": [
          "A rotation is a transformation that spins a figure clockwise or counterclockwise about a fixed point for a given angle and a given direction.",
          "An angle of rotation is the amount of clockwise or counterclockwise rotation about a fixed point.",
          "The point of rotation can be a point on the figure, in the figure, or not on the figure"
